  "keyFeatures": [
    "Tailwind CSS integration for rapid email development",
    "PostHTML-based templating with components and expressions",
    "Email-specific CSS transformers (inlining, purging, shorthand)",
    "CLI tool for scaffolding and building projects",
    "Programmatic API for rendering emails",
    "Multiple build environments with JavaScript configuration",
    "Markdown support with GitHub Flavored Markdown",
    "VML component support for Outlook compatibility"
